  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<java.lang.Object,java.lang.Object>

    public class AdminClientConfiguration
extends ClientConfiguration
    Kinetic admin Client configuration.

    Kinetic admin applications construct a new instance of this instance and set appropriate configurations. Application then calls KineticAdminClientFactory.createInstance(AdminClientConfiguration) to create a new instance of KineticAdminClient

    Author:
    James Hughes., Chiaming Yang
    See Also:
    KineticAdminClientFactory.createInstance(AdminClientConfiguration), KineticAdminClient, Serialized Form
